trans-unit.source: hwtypes - Python implementations of fixed size hardware types
trans-unit.target: hwtypes - Python implementations of fixed size hardware types

trans-unit.source: This library contains data types of fixed bit size and utils for bit manipulations. It also contains types with support for tri state values etc. (Python equivalents of VHDL std_logic_vector, Verilog wire/reg.)
trans-unit.target: This library contains data types of fixed bit size and utils for bit manipulations. It also contains types with support for tri state values etc. (Python equivalents of VHDL std_logic_vector , Verilog wire / reg .)

trans-unit.source: This may be usefull for tools which are simulating hardware or software which needs numbers of exact size.
trans-unit.target: 这可能对模拟硬件或软件的工具有用,因为它们需要精确的尺寸。

trans-unit.source: number types of variable bit size and utils for bit manipulations
trans-unit.target: 可变位的数量类型和位操作的实用工具。
